\pard\tx560\pardeftab560
\f1\fs22 \cf2 Items marked with an empty checkbox are blockers or required actions. Items 1\u8211?4 (icon, privacy policy, in-app privacy link, screenshots) are hard blockers \u8212? submission will fail without them.\par\par

